por uma bola de beisebol.

00:14:09.848 --> 00:14:10.848
O quê?

00:14:11.917 --> 00:14:13.118
Quem te disse isso?

00:14:13.786 --> 00:14:14.786
O papai.

00:14:15.821 --> 00:14:16.821
Clark.

00:14:22.127 --> 00:14:23.896
